SUMMARY:UTOPIA
DESCRIPTION:Tongue in cheek and full of heart.   \nRavi blends unapologetic observational humour and unfiltered storytelling to take us on a deeply personal journey through the messy\, hilarious and strange realities of growing up Dalit\, in and around Mumbai. \nBorn in the City of Dreams and raised on the road\, this show has grown into a love letter to the many complexities of life. Tackling themes of caste\, class\, sex\, love\, feminism and more in his unique voice\, Ravi invites us into his world. \nWith every punchline emerges his version of a perfect Utopia. \nIn collaboration with: \n \n
URL:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/event/utopia/
LOCATION:Bangalore International Centre\, 7\, 4th Main Road\, Domlur II Stage\, Bangalore\, Karnataka\, 560071\, India
CATEGORIES:Performing Arts,Society
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Thumbnail_UTP.jpg
END:VEVENT
